Efficacy of a Decision Aid Consisting of a Video and Booklet on Advance Care 
Planning for Advanced Cancer Patients: Randomized Controlled Trial.

Yun YH(1), Kang E(2), Park S(3), Koh SJ(4), Oh HS(5), Keam B(6), Do YR(7), Chang 
WJ(8), Jeong HS(9), Nam EM(10), Jung KH(11), Kim HR(12), Choo J(13), Lee J(13), 
