Cost Effectiveness of Cladribine Tablets for the Treatment of 
Relapsing-Remitting Multiple Sclerosis in The Netherlands.

Michels RE(1), de Fransesco M(2), Mahajan K(3), Hengstman GJD(4), Schiffers 
