Erratum in
    Appl Health Econ Health Policy. 2020 Feb;18(1):141.

BACKGROUND: Cladribine tablets have recently become available in The Netherlands 
for patients with relapsing-remitting multiple sclerosis (RRMS) as a 
disease-modifying agent that reduces the frequency and severity of relapses and 
